1. Installed `nvm` using the command:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Exited and reopened the terminal to apply changes.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using `nvm install 20.16`.

4. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using `npm install sass@3.7.4`.
